Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.50,0:01:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.97,0:01:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 明天大家一起去哪渡假吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.24,0:01:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得的黄金假期却没安排什么节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.85,0:01:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那多无聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.38,0:01:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得嘛 一起出去走走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.82,0:01:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然说些莫名其妙的话 你是不是醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.06,0:01:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这个人是千杯不醉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.73,0:01:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正你从来也没清醒过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.13,0:01:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走啦 走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.33,0:01:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以去草摩的别墅或借住渡假屋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.47,0:01:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不好啦 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.47,0:01:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.34,0:02:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都说了 我已经去洗过一次温泉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.11,0:02:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那一次我没去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老实说我也很想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好羡慕你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别操纵她！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.19,0:02:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道 知道…所以说你们也会去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.56,0:02:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不可能让我跟小透两人单独相处吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.56,0:02:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过想让我们独处也可以 我不介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.57,0:02:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么就这么决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.24,0:02:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咱们去渡假吧 我负责开车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.64,0:02:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴 你有驾照吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.75,0:02:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想应该有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.98,0:02:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛还要想呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.22,0:02:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样 我们决定去草摩的别墅渡假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本是波鸟开车嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 这里有个湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮、好大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湖值得你这么大惊小怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.47,0:03:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 因为这是我第一次亲眼看到湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.17,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这别墅好像会有"杰森"出没啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.34,0:03:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又说这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说杰森…吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.98,0:03:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰森 杰森是什么来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.89,0:03:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓的杰森就是新种的熊 孤陋寡闻的阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事谁不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.73,0:03:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.09,0:03:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是外国种的熊吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.37,0:03:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.07,0:03:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干嘛突然提出要来这里渡假呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想不透这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八成有什么目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.44,0:03:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是讨厌 你们太疑神疑鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.71,0:03:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的只是想跟大家出来旅行罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到居然会被怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.98,0:03:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有空怀疑别人不如带小透去湖边散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希、阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.49,0:04:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\an8\fs20}静…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.10,0:04:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？你们俩怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气氛很怪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.93,0:04:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我一个人也无妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.04,0:04:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来这里需要一个开朗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 叫绫女来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敢叫他来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就让你下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.32,0:04:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打一开始就乖乖去散步不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.99,0:04:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于你这次突然提出要渡假的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该不会又想欺负催稿人了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.57,0:04:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出去旅行 请别找我 草摩紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个混蛋～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.88,0:04:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有欺负她 只是捉弄她一下罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可怜的催稿人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我突然觉得气氛好僵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.93,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们两人连斗嘴都没兴致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.37,0:05:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该不会是在生我的气吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.64,0:05:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该不会是去扫墓时我说错什么话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或做错什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们两人都很体贴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.68,0:05:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不忍心开口骂我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.19,0:05:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.56,0:05:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实在是太粗心 完全没有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.10,0:05:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管我做错什么请你们尽管说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.27,0:05:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了 你莫名其妙在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 阿夹你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶 这是什么烂路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个脚印…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是杰森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？杰森！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都说了是熊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.95,0:06:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办 糟糕 完了 很危险啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.62,0:06:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们得赶快回去 啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.13,0:06:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.77,0:06:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 没问题 稿子已经好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.14,0:06:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大师 拜托你 我求你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的 我知道了 我挂电话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.41,0:06:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经打给编辑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本来就该这么做 别哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.82,0:06:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多无趣啊 这样不好玩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也觉得不好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.99,0:06:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你有没有受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 拜托你好好注意脚下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.03,0:06:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去捡衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.71,0:07:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说什么好好注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一个摔跤的人凭什么说这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还敢吐槽我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.39,0:07:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次摔得最惨的人是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.96,0:07:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以说养尊处优的少爷最没路用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.89,0:07:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总比每天在山里修行却完全派不上用场的笨蛋来得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才修行四个月怎么可能完全了解山里的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换做是你两天就曝尸荒野了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用这个机会好好学着点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这只笨猫没资格叫我学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁这个机会告诉你啊 杰森不是熊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.21,0:07:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是恐怖片里的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少在那边不懂装懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怖片里出现的熊有什么了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是有够白痴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.45,0:07:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天非干掉你不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.63,0:07:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就听腻这句台词了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.43,0:08:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有种别躲在树上 下来和我对决吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卑鄙的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就目前的体格而言 你比我卑鄙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.54,0:08:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听你在那边胡说 居然叫这么多同伙来助阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也没办法呀 是他们自己要来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.01,0:08:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是遗憾 看来这座山里没有你的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.95,0:08:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶 所以我说老鼠最贼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个真的很爱吵呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.50,0:08:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.00,0:08:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们吵得正凶 我却笑了 实在太失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.81,0:08:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…我总算安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.61,0:08:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们终于恢复过去的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.75,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想到这里我总算放心 就忍不住笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是奇怪呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.23,0:09:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你刚刚摔跤前所说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我们并没有生你的气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我们看起来像生气的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.64,0:09:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实只是不太顺罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.61,0:09:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这样能在一起 感觉上好自然好理所当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.38,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己也是在不知不觉中慢慢依赖起你来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.06,0:09:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你千万别这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.29,0:09:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.96,0:09:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 让你担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.74,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是 我也没在生气喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.27,0:09:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.81,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是我也一样不太顺罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是说你脑子不顺吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.88,0:09:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.56,0:10:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.99,0:10:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.29,0:10:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才是呢 一个人胡思乱想把事情闹这么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 我现在真的好开心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.07,0:10:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…你们不顺 我不该说高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.51,0:10:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 像这样大家在一起 感觉上好自然好理所当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.98,0:10:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也因这样觉得不顺时就让它不顺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.52,0:10:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以后也是 如果你们觉得不顺那就让它不顺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…这么说也很奇怪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.19,0:10:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换句话说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.02,0:10:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是说你们不顺是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是说你们都很好没什么改变 这件事情很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么改变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了愈来愈讨厌这家伙之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才是 刚刚说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.27,0:11:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这辈子都讨厌你 死都讨厌你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.34,0:11:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是感激你呀 我跟你同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.09,0:11:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.43,0:11:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到他们吵架我却说好 这话说起来也很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.60,0:11:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 天都快黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 明天再去湖边散步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 准备好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 都准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.65,0:11:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去湖边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可别掉到湖里喔 阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎么可能掉进去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟先生 我们出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.14,0:12:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔 波鸟睡着了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟也会睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.98,0:12:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 只要是人都需要睡眠的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事我也知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想说的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙不像会在人前睡觉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.59,0:12:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说的倒也是啊 真是罕见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.86,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来波鸟在本家承受的压力不小啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.46,0:12:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 请盖这条毯子 否则会感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透真是体贴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对能当个贤妻良母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.70,0:12:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我哪有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.61,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.24,0:12:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开口赞美别人是个美德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.08,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈哈 大家怎么了 突然都呆住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你突然现身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛 毫无征兆 到底从哪里冒出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.76,0:12:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这还用问吗 当然是从门走进来的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.63,0:12:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹真是名符其实的大白痴呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴 你最没资格说我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 绫女你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 危险 别靠近他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.87,0:13:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 很高兴看到你们因跟我重逢流下感动之泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过还是请你们稍微冷静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.61,0:13:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是得某人的协助才能站在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.58,0:13:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.41,0:13:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不是我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用担心 紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.85,0:13:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使全天下人都视你为敌 我也会站在你这一边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.86,0:13:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女 你才是我心灵的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.03,0:13:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爱你 我的爱 祝你顺风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爱你 我的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.03,0:13:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\an8\fs20}法语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都说了 你到底是来干嘛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先冷静点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.60,0:13:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某部校园片里的老师也曾说过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.07,0:13:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"人"这个字是由两人互相扶持所构成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是句好对白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只是想说说看而已吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好累喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有你在 真的很累人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.39,0:14:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事就回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.33,0:14:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我当然永远都有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.33,0:14:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天就让我们兄弟之情更加深入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这之前 我会先让你沉入湖底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.11,0:14:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗 这样啊 咱们兄弟将形影相随
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是一个人去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.18,0:14:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是叫你别造成别人的困扰吗 绫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟先生 你醒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.39,0:14:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵成这样 我怎么可能睡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨 波鸟 早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真抱歉 吵醒你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也叫自己安静点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.97,0:14:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何会来这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.54,0:14:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去本家后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.54,0:14:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个53岁的工人告诉我 你跟大家一起来别墅渡假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然这样 那我也想参与 所以就来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这么跟来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.18,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在波鸟面前说话就这么坦诚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希、阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.25,0:15:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们今天不是要带小透去湖边散步的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.26,0:15:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.06,0:15:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.16,0:15:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样吗 既然如此 那就快点去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.00,0:15:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽不知道你们在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.34,0:15:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但既然要保护女性就该更机灵点才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不都是你这家伙害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.91,0:15:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我们就去湖边散步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是群麻烦的年轻人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.09,0:15:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还以为你一定会跟去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.29,0:15:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么啊 紫吴 我才没那么不通情理呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.66,0:15:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且好久没三个人聚一聚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.50,0:15:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么 今晚我不会让你睡的 紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女 这是我的荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到今晚可以跟你做同样的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们怎么老玩不腻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.98,0:16:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉好清爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.59,0:16:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙今晚要睡这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.26,0:16:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是你老哥 你想办法处理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.69,0:16:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能的话我早做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最讨厌那种只知道靠别人的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.67,0:16:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你呢 还不是老靠着紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事跟你无关吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说的好像你都知道似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.94,0:16:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才懒得知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.98,0:16:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁叫你老在我面前晃 我不想看到你都不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你不会消失吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很想消失啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我为何非得跟你来湖边不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.15,0:16:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是 跟你来湖边对我而言是件多痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！这种地方多无聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.93,0:16:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可别误会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.20,0:16:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们并不讨厌来湖边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是讨厌跟这家伙来罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.44,0:17:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.51,0:17:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…那就好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.15,0:17:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你没误会就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.85,0:17:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真漂亮呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们在湖边绕一圈好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.53,0:17:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.83,0:17:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.07,0:17:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照片 是佳菜婚礼的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看或不看是你的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.34,0:17:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她结婚了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然说要来别墅 我还以为怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.72,0:17:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.62,0:17:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你担心了 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.62,0:17:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直觉得应该告诉你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.03,0:18:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你冲到婚礼上从新郎手中把佳菜抢过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 紫吴说不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经挽回不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.01,0:18:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟佳菜已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.41,0:18:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以说 这照片也不看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我无法接受这个结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.39,0:18:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是站在波鸟这一边的人 所以有话直说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.56,0:18:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我无法接受这样的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佳菜太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为她可以忘记一切 捉住自己的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你呢 却得背负所有的不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.14,0:18:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你被她遗弃 被她利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.95,0:18:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你觉得等雪融化之后会变成什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会变成春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不全然是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你实在是太温柔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.47,0:19:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽说这也是你的优点 但你太体贴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.91,0:19:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为这样才老受些不必要受的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.54,0:19:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会叫你跟佳菜破镜重圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.25,0:19:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我敢拍胸脯的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望能让你得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.75,0:19:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比佳菜还多一千倍、两千倍的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.66,0:19:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种强势的态度真该让由希看看才对呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次若能认识一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.27,0:19:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在一起时也不会觉得孤单的对象就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在一起就等于幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.98,0:19:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是紫吴 有诗人的气质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小说家 小说家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.41,0:19:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的对象啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.52,0:20:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对被诅咒的十二生肖的人而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个愿望可能有点无理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.69,0:20:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了…\N他们回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仔细想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.46,0:20:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能跟佳菜有这么一段情 我也该心满意足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.80,0:20:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我而言这样就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.21,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我唯一能做的就是希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.91,0:20:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别让他们跟我有相同的遭遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎你们回来了 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有其他伙伴们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁是他的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.72,0:20:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚我接受了波鸟的建议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.39,0:20:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后要用强势的态度和你加深感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.06,0:20:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么叫强势的态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.87,0:20:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说 由希是我弟弟 我是由希的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.07,0:20:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这是个事实 我要在此向大家宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.74,0:21:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 你必须服从我这个哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.38,0:21:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇～～～～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女那家伙还是没搞懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他还是没搞懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！！怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.00,0:21:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 绫女变成一条蛇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种东西丢了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.61,0:21:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然对变成蛇的绫女感到有点抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.31,0:21:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过引起这样的骚动 我真的很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.72,0:21:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我多希望这种愉快的日子能一直持续下去啊

